{
  "page": "Lord Commander",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Lord Commander</b> is the senior officer of multiple organizations. These include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_King%27s_Landing#Known_Commanders_of_the_City_Watch\" title=\"City Watch of King&#39;s Landing\">Commander of the City Watch of King's Landing</a></li>\n<li>Lord Commander of the <a href=\"/index.php/City_Watch_of_Oldtown\" title=\"City Watch of Oldtown\">City Watch of Oldtown</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Kingsguard\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Kingsguard\">Lord Commander of the Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander of the Night's Watch</a></li>\n<li>Lord Commander of the <a href=\"/index.php/Queensguard\" title=\"Queensguard\">Queensguard</a></li>\n<li>Lord Commander of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rainbow_Guard\" title=\"Rainbow Guard\">Rainbow Guard</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Commander&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander%27s_Tower\" title=\"Lord Commander&#39;s Tower\">Lord Commander's Tower</a>, a tower of Castle Black.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404170236\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnst